text: Gyula Kunszt (31 July 1903 - 22 December 1991) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1903 births Category:1991 deaths Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
